    <Content contentid="4259" contenttypeid="STAFF" desc="Staff">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>One of the many delights of staying in a private villa is the personalised service guests enjoy. Villa Seascape’s gracious, well-trained team are on hand whenever required, and otherwise stay discreetly behind the scenes respecting guests’ privacy. All take pleasure in delighting guests with warm, friendly Bali-style hospitality.</p>]]></Description>
